Message:
Remove dependency on passport-twitter, remove twitter-lite and twitter example

@passport-js/passport-twitter had already replaced passport-twitter in a prior commit.
Twitter has discontinued free to use APIs for getting tweets, and many other previously free to use data.  With this commit, hackathon-starter will only support login by twitter out of the box.  twitter-lite was used for the API example and is no longer applicable, hence being removed with this commit. Developers that have a paid twitter account can add twitter API support based on their need and twitter subscription.
